ware/systemd/man/systemd.network.html#AddressAutoconfiguration=3D">=C2=B6</=
a></dt><dd><p>Boolean values to specify whether IPv6 addresses can be
        autoconfigured with this prefix and whether the prefix can be used =
for
        onlink determination. Both settings default to "<code class=3D"lite=
ral">true</code>"
