        </p></dd><dt id=3D"Prefix=3D1"><span class=3D"term"><code class=3D"=
varname">Prefix=3D</code></span><a class=3D"headerlink" title=3D"Permalink =
to this term" href=3D"https://www.freedesktop.org/software/systemd/man/syst=
emd.network.html#Prefix=3D1">=C2=B6</a></dt><dd><p>The IPv6 prefix that is =
to be distributed to hosts.
        Similarly to configuring static IPv6 addresses, the setting is
