eadline" href=3D"https://www.freedesktop.org/software/systemd/man/systemd.n=
etwork.html#%5BBridge%5D%20Section%20Options">=C2=B6</a></h2><p>The "<code =
class=3D"literal">[Bridge]</code>" section accepts the
