p.org/software/systemd/man/systemd.network.html#UseBPDU=3D">=C2=B6</a></dt>=
<dd><p>A boolean. Configures whether STP Bridge Protocol Data Units will be
            processed by the bridge port. Defaults to yes.</p></dd><dt id=
=3D"FastLeave=3D"><span class=3D"term"><code class=3D"varname">FastLeave=3D=
</code></span><a class=3D"headerlink" title=3D"Permalink to this term" href=
=3D"https://www.freedesktop.org/software/systemd/man/systemd.network.html#F=
astLeave=3D">=C2=B6</a></dt><dd><p>A boolean. This flag allows the bridge t=
o immediately stop multicast
