      </pre><pre class=3D"programlisting">/etc/systemd/network/25-tunnel-vt=
i.netdev
[NetDev]
Name=3Dvti-tun
Kind=3Dvti
      </pre><p>This will bring interface "<code class=3D"literal">ens1</cod=
