      a SIT tunnel, a GRE tunnel, and a VTI tunnel using it.</p></div></div=
><br class=3D"example-break"><div class=3D"example"><a name=3D"id-1.21.7"><=
/a><p class=3D"title"><b>Example&nbsp;6.&nbsp;A bond device</b></p><div cla=
ss=3D"example-contents"><pre class=3D"programlisting"># /etc/systemd/networ=
k/30-bond1.network
[Match]
Name=3Dbond1

[Network]
DHCP=3Dipv6
</pre><pre class=3D"programlisting"># /etc/systemd/network/30-bond1.netdev
[NetDev]
