</pre><pre class=3D"programlisting"># /etc/systemd/network/30-bond1-dev2.ne=
twork
[Match]
MACAddress=3D52:54:00:e9:64:42

[Network]
Bond=3Dbond1
</pre><p>This will create a bond device "<code class=3D"literal">bond1</cod=
